    "preview": "{\"text\": \"<!--StartFragment--><meta charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"><b style=\\\"font-weight:normal;\\\" id=\\\"docs-internal-guid-032e30b9-7fff-0951-8df5-ee29ad626f6e\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">30+ years of audacious turnarounds, market-shaping telematics, and people-first leadership deserved more than a farewell speech, so the client asked us to turn Vipen Malhotra\u2019s career into an heirloom coffee-table book. Working against a ceremony-locked deadline, our writers, designers, and print engineers sifted thousands of photos, project memos, and personal anecdotes to produce a 120-page volume that feels as intimate as a family album yet as authoritative as an annual report. It honours the impact he\u2019s had on organisations </span><span style=\\\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">and</span><span style=\\\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\"> on lives, capturing the perseverance, innovation, and empathy colleagues credit for their own growth.</span></b><!--EndFragment-->\", \"summary\": \"<!--StartFragment--><meta charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"><b style=\\\"font-weight:normal;\\\" id=\\\"docs-internal-guid-233adbbc-7fff-8180-2ad0-f96792bb4435\\\"><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">When a leading telecom company approached us,</span><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\"> they wanted something to honour one of their best leaders with something that their legacy truly deserved &amp; not just another farewell video or speech.</span></p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">They wanted a living tribute - something that would preserve three decades of Vipen Malhotra\u2019s leadership, vision, and human touch.</span></p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">That vision led towards turning thousands of photos, reports, and memories into a coffee-table heirloom: a 120-page keepsake that would feel as intimate as a family album yet as authoritative as a corporate chronicle.</span></p></b><br class=\\\"Apple-interchange-newline\\\"><!--EndFragment-->\", \"projectSnapshots\": [\"<!--StartFragment--><meta charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"><b style=\\\"font-weight:normal;\\\" id=\\\"docs-internal-guid-d2e93ca6-7fff-333f-8172-2522b555deca\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">Turned a \u201cshut it down\u201d order into a comeback story</span><span style=\\\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">, reviving Syntel, protecting thousands of jobs, and rebuilding trust in the brand.</span></b><!--EndFragment-->\", \"<!--StartFragment--><meta charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"><b style=\\\"font-weight:normal;\\\" id=\\\"docs-internal-guid-84f2ee73-7fff-46ae-071f-25973773a635\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">Pushed India\u2019s telematics frontier forward</span><span style=\\\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">, rolling out 100k+ GPS units that now keep smart-city fleets and long-haul trucks running on time.</span></b><!--EndFragment-->\", \"<!--StartFragment--><meta charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"><b style=\\\"font-weight:normal;\\\" id=\\\"docs-internal-guid-a7991e55-7fff-5e40-4e86-372dd232185b\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">Led with quiet empathy</span><span style=\\\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">, from salary sacrifices in tough cycles to life-saving support for an employee\u2019s family, he made compassion a core policy.</span></b><!--EndFragment-->\"]}",
